          <p class="text-gray-700">Framer landing page with brutalist value prop: "Stop wasting 10 hours every week on client reports. Automate them in 10 minutes with ReportGenie." Specific problem, specific solution. 60-second demo video above the fold showing: upload data ‚Üí generate report ‚Üí email client. Transparent pricing: "Starter $49/month, Pro $149/month" with features. One-click trial: "Start Free Trial - No Credit Card Required." Social proof: "Used by 500+ agencies" with logos.</p>
