        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 border-l-[3px] border-red-500 rounded-r">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">‚ùå Pricing Hidden or Unclear</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">"Contact Sales" = expensive = skip. Transparent pricing visible = can afford = start trial. Pricing visible = 67% higher conversion.</p>
