              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">SaaS had screenshots only. Added 60-second demo video prominently. Month 1: 6x more trial signups. Video = see it work = want it = sign up.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-indigo-600 font-black text-2xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Value prop clear: 4x better visitor fit</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">Added "Stop wasting time on X, automate with Y" prominently. Month 1: 4x more qualified trials. Clear value = solves my problem = sign up.</p>
