          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Squarespace: Quick MVP</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Clean templates, easy pricing pages, integrated signup forms. Fast setup for early-stage SaaS. Basic but functional.</p>
