        </div>

        <div class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 pb-6">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Should I show pricing on my SaaS site?</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Yes. Transparent pricing = can afford = sign up. "Contact Sales" = expensive = skip. Even if pricing is complex, show starting price with "Custom pricing for enterprises" below. Pricing visible = 67% higher conversion. Hide pricing = hide trust = lose conversions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 pb-6">
